Package fr.ign.artiscales.tools.parameter

Class ProfileUrbanFabric

java.lang.Object
fr.ign.artiscales.tools.parameter.ProfileUrbanFabric
public class ProfileUrbanFabric
extends java.lang.Object
Parameters describing an urban fabric. One different objects for each of the simulated urban scene. Must be set in a .json file and then parse into either constructor or static parser method.
